 S/14170 Rifleman Harry Timberlake of the 8 Bn Rifle Bde KIA 15th September 1916 in the Delvelle Wood Area of the Somme .
 He was my great uncle on my mothers side, Brother of William John Timberlake my Grandfather  . He was born in 1884 in Cheslea (London ) . He was married to Miss Lile Longman in 1911 in Fulham and had a Daughter Eileen who died in 1922
